task.summary: First commit after git trouble. Hoping all is ok on master.
Gave the model thread a name for easier debugging
Removed long encoding of (x, y) pair of coordinates. Replaced with separate x, y variables.
Removed long encoding of (x, y) pair of coordinates. Replaced with separate x, y variables. Removed leftover code.
Replaced field variable with local variable in appropiate method
Migrated Pins and Components from Component.BehaviourSpecification to the more general LibComponent.
Access level for method changed from public to package-private
Adding new components to schematic. WIP.
Partially fixed adding new elements to simulation
Fixed mouse button up from being registered as button down
Components can now be added correctly
Added a constant to represent the select radius of a termination
Wires can be created by draging off a termination. Added a getter method for terminations in Component to make them accessible for wiring operations
Set editMode to permanent true for testing purposes. editMode will be dynamically set to th right value when visualization mode will be made available
Drawing code no longer relies on attach/detach flags
Reorder calls to avoid null values in places where null should not appear
Wire width must be divided by two to get radius
Redraw is requested when new wires are being added
Fixed decision whether new wires are vertical or horizontal
